{"tid":650196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【普教中/諷刺/散文】《三個女人》","createTime":"2018-05-02T06:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T10:34:36.000Z","uid":180575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94bea332c370fd7e1f934875192c2b28189abc2e","tid":650196,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港的教育局好像有人說：<br />\n粵語只是方言不能視為母語。<br />\n<br />\n媽媽只是我最常見的女人不能視為母親，<br />\n所以媽媽不是母親。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我的母親可能是我爸爸在內地的二奶，<br />\n或是遠在英國的三奶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得爸爸曾說：你媽媽就是糟糠之妻必可棄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n我嘗試模擬「我的童話日記」中6歲主角的思維和說話模式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n【網上熱話】教育局派普通話課程配套資料　有篇章稱粵語只是方言不是母語<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180501/s00001/1525166632846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180501%2Fs00001%2F1525166632846&d=s6A8is8SmS4uq86RsauOtAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=16a25376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180501%2Fs00001%2F1525166632846&h=9360a437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180501/s00001/1525166632846</a><br />\n<br />\n【網上熱話】粵語只是方言？港大謝錫金：父母說的就是母語<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180501/s00001/1525187565711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180501%2Fs00001%2F1525187565711&d=s6A8is8SmS4uq86RsauOtAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=10208f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2F